For the food, it may be a little too expensive for some people, but it sure is justified with the kind of place. The quality of food may vary , on some days its good, others a bit disappointing but never bad. One minor inconvenience, it's hella popular and sometimes there so much people packed in there, with all the noises.
All in all, if you're in for the day at this city, that's your place to go.

Firstly I want to make a small remark about the reception which was a little frosty and not up to par.
secondly, the waitress brings us a menu for three people which is not normal for a self-respecting restaurant.
then the service is too slow and the waitresses are not up to standard.
too much noise and laughing between colleagues which is not serious for my taste, and the music was too loud it felt like we were in a discotheque.
in the room as in the terrace it was cold and it was very unpleasant.
the dishes were catastrophic, the burger was poor quality and not spicy... only the pizza was good 
I give an overall rating of 5/10 and I don't recommend the place since it was a bad experience and we were very disappointed.
